sentiment_score_definition: x <= -0.35: Bearish; -0.35 < x <= -0.15: Somewhat-Bearish; -0.15 < x < 0.15: Neutral; 0.15 <= x < 0.35: Somewhat_Bullish; x >= 0.35: Bullish
relevance_score_definition: 0 < x <= 1, with a higher score indicating higher relevance.

feed.title: Cottage cheese recalled from MS Walmart stores over health risks. See if you bought any
feed.summary: Certain Great Value brand cottage cheese products sold at Walmart stores in Mississippi and 23 other states have been voluntarily recalled due to potential pasteurization issues. The unpasteurized dairy ingredients could pose serious health risks from bacteria like Salmonella or E. coli. Consumers who purchased the affected products between February 17th and 20th are advised not to consume them and to return them for a full refund.
